Invocation Name: college eight ball
des: Are you ready for college, yet don't know where you could possibly qualify for? Well, thanks to College8Ball you can find specific schools in California that may accept you. The trick to this is answering a few questions about your scores and you will receive a list of the top California universities and colleges that can accept you. So go ahead and start your researching today!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
